  "keyFeatures": [
    "Specify CLI for project bootstrapping with multiple AI agent support",
    "Structured specification templates for intent-driven development",
    "Slash commands workflow for specification → planning → tasks → implementation",
    "Support for 15+ AI coding agents (Claude, Gemini, Copilot, Cursor, etc.)",
    "Constitution-based project governance and development principles",
    "Automated branch and feature numbering management",
    "Quality checklists for specification and plan validation",
    "Extension system for custom workflow integrations",
    "Cross-platform script support (Bash/PowerShell)",
    "Template-driven document generation"
  ],
